name: Kristina Kostenko
description: I am passionate, cheerful, active, sociable, open and responsive girl. Perhaps that is why my life is painted in bright colors. I always have something to do because I do not like to sit still and do nothing. I also love to cook, it’s my passion. I love to receive visitors and so I like to surprise them with my culinary skills. I dream of traveling! I am confident that this is a special place in human life. I would very much like to visit many countries to see the world and learn the traditions and culture of the peoples of the world! I love the sea, mountains, nature, because they fill my life with bright emotions and inspire. I also love sports and prefer to keep my body in good shape. I am a feminine, kind, loyal and sexy. I appreciate honesty and reliability. I find it hard to put up with the cruelty and injustice. I like to always be in good shape, to achieve your goals and never lose heart.
